text: Miguel Eduardo Caneo (born August 17, 1983 in General Roca in Rio Negro Province) is an Argentine football midfielder, who currently plays for Boca Unidos. ==Career== As a young boy he was part of the Boca Juniors youth system, to make his professional debut in the first team in 2003. He made a total of 33 appearances for the club in all competitions, scoring 2 goals. He was then transferred to Argentine club Quilmes in 2005 before joining Colo- Colo in 2006.
